titles.title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a technical correction in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3910.

action.text: Mr. Hansen asked unanimous consent to take from the Speaker's table and consider.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 10/15/1998--Introduced. Makes technical corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 3910 (Automobile National Heritage Area, Michigan).
